ns\tSafety, pain, cost, results in under 60 seconds\tTop 3-5 buyer objections\tHigher conversion rates\tSonoBello: $3.1M spend Social Proof Structure\tSpecific numbers + real names + outcomes\t\"Jennifer: $8,200 → $147,000\"\tCustomer success data\tCredibility boost, purchase justification\tLegal ad case study Offer Stack Formula\t4-6 bonuses + discount + urgency + guarantee\t56% off + free wipes + face lotion + mystery gift + free shipping\tProduct/service ecosystem\tHigher AOV, reduced price resistance\tMultiple examples CTA Optimization\tLow-friction micro-commitment\t\"5-question quiz\" vs \"schedule consultation\"\tSimple next step\tHigher conversion rates\tLegal: quiz vs call 🎬 Niche-Specific Script Templates Health/Beauty/Fitness (90-second format) Hook: Transformation promise with visual proof (0-15s) Mechanism: Expert explanation with authority anchor (15-30s) Objection Stack: 3-4 rapid testimonials (30-60s) Offer: Stacked bonuses with urgency (60-80s) CTA: Risk-free trial or consultation (80-90s) Legal/Financial Services (60-second format) Hook: Self-assessment checklist (0-10s) Villain: Position against common enemy (10-25s) Social Proof: Specific case outcomes (25-45s) CTA: Low-friction quiz/assessment (45-60s) E-commerce Products (Short-form) Hook: Social tension or visible outcome (0-5s) Demo: Product in action with instant proof (5-20s) Authority: Brief expert validation (20-30s) Offer: Limited-time stack with guarantee (30-45s) 🤖 AI Agent Development Specifications Core AI Agent Capabilities Required: Function\tInput Requirements\tProcessing Logic\tOutput Format Niche Analysis\tTarget audience, product type, price point\tIdentify top 3 pain points, buying objections, emotional triggers\tStructured analysis report Hook Generation\tProduct benefits, target demo, emotional triggers\tApply 7 hook formulas with A/B variations\t5-10 hook options per formula Script Structure\tNiche, ad length, platform, conversion goal\tSelect optimal template and customize